<div><head>楚竹書十三《彭祖》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.2">耈老問于彭祖曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.3">「氏執心不忘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.4">受命永長。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.5">臣何藝可行，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.6">而營於朕身，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.7">而謐于帝嘗？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.8">彭祖曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.9">「休哉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.10">乃將多問因由，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.11">乃不失度。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.12">彼天之道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.13">唯恒<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.14">言：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.15">天地與人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.16">若經與緯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.17">若表與裏。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.18">問曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.19">「三去其二，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.20">豈若已？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.21">彭祖曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.22">「吁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.23">汝孳孳布問，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.24">余告汝人倫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.25">曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.26">戒之毋驕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.27">慎終保勞。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.28">大匡之要，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.29">難易滯欲。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.30">余告汝□，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.31">不知所終。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.32">耈老曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.33">「眊眊余朕孳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.34">未則于天，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.35">敢問為人？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.36">彭祖曰既躋於天，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.37">又墜於淵。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.38">夫子之德登矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.39">何其崇。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.40">故君之願，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.41">良父子兄弟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.42">五紀畢周，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.43">雖貧必修。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.44">五紀不工，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.45">雖富必失。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.46">余告汝禍<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.47">□□之謀不可行，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.48">怵惕之心不可長，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.49">遠慮用素，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.50">心白身釋。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.51">余告汝咎，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.52">□者不以，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.53">多務者多憂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.54">賊者自賊也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.55">彭祖曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.56">一命一修，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.57">是謂益愈。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.58">一命三修，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.59">是謂自厚。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.60">三命四修，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.61">是謂百姓之主。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.62">一命一䑋，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.63">是謂遭殃。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.64">一命三䑋是謂不長。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.65">三命四䑋，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.66">是謂絕輟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.67">毋抽富，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.68">毋訶賢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.69">毋向梪。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.70">耈老二拜稽首曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.71">「朕孳不敏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.72">既得聞道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4541_CHANT_001-1a.73">恐弗能守。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
